import React from 'react'

import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import {
  ReactComponent as Logo
} from '../../assets/fake-logo.svg'

import {
  HeaderContainer,
  OptionsContainer
} from './header.styles'

const Header = () => (
  <HeaderContainer>
    <Link to='/'>
      <Logo />
    </Link>
    <OptionsContainer>
      <Link to='/shop'>
        Shop
      </Link>
      <Link to='/contact'>
        Contact
      </Link>
    </OptionsContainer>
  </HeaderContainer>
)

export default Header
